Privacy Policy for Grand Mountain Adventure

Last updated: [7/24/23]

[RageStudioRus] ("we," "our," or "us") is the developer of the mobile game "Grand Mountain Adventure" ("the game"), available on the Google Play Store.

This Privacy Policy is intended to inform you about the types of information we may collect from users of our game and how we may use and protect that information. By using the game, you agree to the collection and use of information as described in this Privacy Policy.

Information We Collect

Personal Information:
We do not collect any personally identifiable information (PII), such as your name, email address, or contact information, through the game.

Non-Personal Information:
During gameplay, the game may collect non-personal information that does not directly identify you. This information may include:

Device Information: We may collect information about your device, including its model, operating system version, unique device identifiers, and other technical data.

Gameplay Data: We may collect information about your interactions with the game, such as your progress, achievements, and gameplay statistics.

Log Information: Our servers automatically log certain information when you access or use the game, including your IP address, browser type, and the date and time of your interactions.

Cookies and Similar Technologies: The game may use cookies or similar technologies to enhance your experience and collect non-personal information.

How We Use Your Information

Improve Gameplay: We may use the collected non-personal information to analyze and improve gameplay, troubleshoot technical issues, and optimize in-game features.

Analytics: We may use analytics tools to understand user behavior and preferences, which helps us enhance the game's overall performance and experience.

Marketing: We do not use your information for marketing purposes, and we will not share your information with third-party advertisers.

Information Sharing

We do not share your personal or non-personal information with third parties, except as described in this Privacy Policy. In the event of a merger, acquisition, or sale of our company or assets, your information may be transferred to the new owners, subject to this Privacy Policy.

Data Security

We take reasonable measures to protect the information collected through the game. However, please be aware that no data transmission over the internet or electronic storage method is entirely secure.

Children's Privacy

The game is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe your child has provided us with personal information, please contact us, and we will delete such information from our records.

Changes to this Privacy Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our data practices. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at [RageStudioRus@gmail.com].
